            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-12-31T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-06-25T11:00:00-05:00" n="570" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d570">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On August 13, the Department of State issued to the press a statement responding
                    to a number of charges made against the United States by Marshal Tito in the
                    course of an interview with the official Yugoslav news agency on August 7. For
                    the text of the statement, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, August 24, 1947, page 391.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
